	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So im pretty new to this nes dev stuff.<br />i am just starting to learn nes asm.<br />i have learned many of the very basics like the memory adresses and how hex and binary numbers work and im just starting to learn how to program the ppu.<br />im wondering what the best nes asm compiler is...any recommendations?

		

		</td>
