	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />&quot;Nesasm&quot; uses non-standard syntax for zeropage instructions, so avoid it.<br /><br />I like to use ASM6, because it's simple, but different people have different preferences.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


